es\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willie_Jones_(third_baseman)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willie_Jones_(third_baseman)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The clip\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"Beyonc\\u00e9'sCowboy Cartersong\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"Fun\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"footage\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 351}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us talk about power because, really, that's what this story is about,\\\" Beyonc\\u00e9 says.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.303674136542616e-17, \"text\": \"Beyonc\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XLVII_halftime_show\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Physical power, its beauty, its wonder, the way it never stops amazing you.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Physical power\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"its beauty\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"its wonder\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there is spiritual power, the kind that really matters.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spiritual power\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The power you can not see, only sense.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The power\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \", only sense\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The power you need in those moments when life goes a little sideways on you.\\\"\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The power\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"those moments\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"a little sideways\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video includes clips of Biles at the 2021 Tokyo Olympics, where she notably withdrew from the competition.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The video\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"clips\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And, of course, lasting power,\\\" Beyonc\\u00e9 continues.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"Beyonc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Only a select few know what it feels like to get to the top and stay there and somehow keep getting better.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles inspires me, and I am pretty sure she inspires you, too.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such confidence in her strength, such beauty in her power, such a great lesson in her story.\", 